---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import drawingImg from '../assets/drawing/rocky-ocean-drawing.png';
---

<section id="om-baten" class="about">
  <div class="about-inner container">

    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="section-label">About the boat</p>
      <h2 class="display about-title">A boat built<br/>to sail</h2>

      <div class="about-body">
        <p>
          Rocky Ocean is a one-off 36-foot Cruiser/Racer designed and built by H. Aaslestad
          in 2005. From day one she has been rigged for racing – with entries in the
          Shetland Race, 2 Star and Ferderseilasen – and still carries the character of a
          boat seriously built to go fast.
        </p>
        <p>
          In the summer of 2025 she was purchased in Bergen and brought up to Ålesund,
          where she now serves as a permanent base. The boat is used as home and office
          by her owner, who studies naval architecture at NTNU – a fitting choice for
          someone living close to hull lines and sail trim every day.
        </p>
        <p>
          The vision going forward is a modern Cruiser/Racer expression: bowsprit, new
          mainsail cover and headsail cover in navy blue, sprayhood and sandblasted
          stanchions. Minimalist, safe and ready for offshore passages.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-tags">
        <span>Shetland Race</span>
        <span>2 Star</span>
        <span>Ferderseilasen</span>
        <span>Cruiser / Racer</span>
        <span>Ålesund</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-visual">
      <Image
        src={drawingImg}
        alt="Rocky Ocean – linjetegning"
        widths={[600, 900]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw"
        class="about-drawing"
      />
      <div class="about-stat-row">
        <div class="about-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">2005</span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">Byggeår</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">36<small>fot</small></span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">Lengde</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">One-off</span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">Klasse</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--section-pad);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.2rem);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 48ch;
  }

  .about-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-tags span {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  .about-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .about-drawing {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    opacity: 0.88;
  }

  .about-stat-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .about-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-num small {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-left: 0.15rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .stat-lbl {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }
    .about-body { max-width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
